Package: surrosurvo
Type: Package
Title: Evaluation of Individual-Level Surrogacy for Survival and Ordinal,
  Continuous, or Survival Endpoints
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-07-07
Authors@R: c(
  person("Kengo", "Nagashima", email = "nshi1201@gmail.com",
         role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4529-9045")),
  person("Jun", "Okui", role = c("aut")))
Description: An implementation of estimators of Kendall's tau for survival data:
  Oakes (1982)'s non-parametric estimator <doi:10.1111/j.2517-6161.1982.tb01222.x>,
  Lakhal et al. (2009)'s inverse probability weighting (IPCW) estimators
  <doi:10.2202/1557-4679.1121>, Okui et al. (2025)'s modified
  IPCW estimator <doi:10.1093/bjs/znaf131>, and theses extensions
  of stratified estimators.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: stats, survival, Rcpp (>= 1.0.13), copula, pimeta
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://nshi-stat.github.io/surrosurvo/
